---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — TIP TIG"
  description="Privacy policy for tiptig.com — how we handle your data, your rights under GDPR, and our commitment to data protection. No tracking, no analytics, no third-party cookies."
>
  <section class="pv-hero">
    <div class="pv-hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="pv-eyebrow">Datenschutzerklärung</div>
      <h1>Privacy<br><span class="blue">Policy</span></h1>
      <p class="pv-desc">
        How we handle your data — transparently and in full compliance with the
        EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pv-content">
    <div class="inner-pv">

      <!-- Data Controller -->
      <div class="pv-section reveal">
        <h2>1. Data Controller</h2>
        <div class="pv-text">
          <p>The controller responsible for data processing on this website pursuant to Art.&nbsp;4(7) GDPR is:</p>
          <div class="pv-contact-block">
            <p>
              <strong>Ing. Siegfried Plasch</strong><br>
              Baumayrweg 4<br>
              4631 Krenglbach, Austria
            </p>
            <p>
              Phone: <a href="tel:+43720303500">+43 720 303500</a><br>
              Email: <a href="mailto:office@tiptig.com">office@tiptig.com</a>
            </p>
          </div>
          <p>
            For any questions regarding data protection or to exercise your rights,
            please contact us at the address above.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Hosting -->
      <div class="pv-section reveal">
        <h2>2. Hosting &amp; Server Log Files</h2>
        <div class="pv-text">
          <p>
            This website is hosted by <strong>Netlify, Inc.</strong> (44 Montgomery Street, Suite 300,
            San Francisco, CA 94104, USA). When you visit this website, Netlify automatically
            collects and stores information in server log files that your browser transmits, including:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>IP address (anonymized where technically possible)</li>
            <li>Date and time of the request</li>
            <li>Requested page / URL</li>
            <li>Referrer URL (the previously visited page)</li>
            <li>Browser type, version, and language</li>
            <li>Operating system</li>
            <li>Amount of data transferred and status code</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            This data is processed on the basis of our legitimate interest in ensuring the secure
            and efficient operation of this website (Art.&nbsp;6(1)(f) GDPR). Log data is retained
            for up to 30 days and is not combined with other data sources.
          </p>
          <p>
            Netlify processes data in the United States. The data transfer is safeguarded by
            Netlify's Data Processing Agreement (DPA) and the EU Standard Contractual Clauses
            (SCCs) pursuant to Art.&nbsp;46(2)(c) GDPR.
            For details, see <a href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Netlify's Privacy Policy</a>
            and <a href="https://www.netlify.com/gdpr-ccpa/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Netlify's GDPR page</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Cookies -->
      <div class="pv-section reveal">
        <h2>3. Cookies</h2>
        <div class="pv-text">
          <p>
            This website does <strong>not</strong> use cookies — neither for tracking, analytics,
            advertising, nor for session management. No data is stored on your device when you
            visit this website.
          </p>
          <p>
            Should we introduce technically necessary cookies in the future (e.g., for a cookie
            consent mechanism itself), this policy will be updated accordingly, and consent will be
            obtained where required.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Analytics -->
      <div class="pv-section reveal">
        <h2>4. Analytics &amp; Tracking</h2>
        <div class="pv-text">
          <p>
            This website does <strong>not</strong> use any analytics or tracking services
            (such as Google Analytics, Matomo, or similar). We do not track your behavior,
            create user profiles, or collect data beyond what is described in Section&nbsp;2.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact Forms -->
      <div class="pv-section reveal">
        <h2>5. Contact Forms &amp; Email Communication</h2>
        <div class="pv-text">
          <p>
            If you contact us via a contact form on this website, by email, or by phone,
            the information you provide (name, email address, message content, and any
            additional details you share) will be processed for the purpose of handling
            your inquiry.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Legal basis:</strong> Processing is based on pre-contractual measures
            at your request (Art.&nbsp;6(1)(b) GDPR) or our legitimate interest in responding
            to inquiries (Art.&nbsp;6(1)(f) GDPR).
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Retention:</strong> Your data will be retained for the duration necessary
            to process your request and, thereafter, for the period required by statutory
            retention obligations (typically up to 7 years under Austrian commercial and tax law).
            Data is deleted once these periods expire and no further legitimate purpose exists.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Web Fonts -->
      <div class="pv-section reveal">
        <h2>6. Web Fonts</h2>
        <div class="pv-text">
          <p>
            All fonts used on this website (Manrope, Inter) are <strong>self-hosted</strong>
            on our own server. No connections to external font services (such as Google Fonts
            or Adobe Fonts) are established when you visit this website. Your IP address is
            not transmitted to any third-party font provider.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Social Media -->
      <div class="pv-section reveal">
        <h2>7. Social Media Links</h2>
        <div class="pv-text">
          <p>
            This website contains links to our profiles on social media platforms
            (YouTube, LinkedIn, Instagram, Facebook, TikTok). These are standard hyperlinks —
            no social media plugins, tracking pixels, or embedded widgets are used.
            No data is transmitted to these platforms until you actively click a link and
            leave our website.
          </p>
          <p>
            Once you visit a third-party platform, their respective privacy policies apply.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Third-Party Content -->
      <div class="pv-section reveal">
        <h2>8. Third-Party Content &amp; Embeds</h2>
        <div class="pv-text">
          <p>
            This website does <strong>not</strong> embed third-party content such as
            YouTube videos, Google Maps, or social media widgets. All content — including
            images, maps, and interactive elements — is served directly from our own infrastructure.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SSL -->
      <div class="pv-section reveal">
        <h2>9. TLS/SSL Encryption</h2>
        <div class="pv-text">
          <p>
            This website uses TLS (Transport Layer Security) encryption for all connections.
            You can identify an encrypted connection by the lock icon in your browser's address
            bar and the "https://" prefix in the URL. When TLS encryption is active, the data
            you transmit to us cannot be read by third parties.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Data Recipients -->
      <div class="pv-section reveal">
        <h2>10. Data Recipients &amp; Transfers</h2>
        <div class="pv-text">
          <p>
            Access to personal data is limited to those who require it for the stated purposes.
            Apart from our hosting provider (Netlify, see Section&nbsp;2), we do not share your
            personal data with third parties unless required by law or necessary for the
            performance of a contract.
          </p>
          <p>
            Where data transfers outside the EU/EEA occur (specifically to Netlify in the USA),
            these are safeguarded by EU Standard Contractual Clauses (SCCs) in accordance with
            Art.&nbsp;46(2)(c) GDPR.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Your Rights -->
      <div class="pv-section reveal">
        <h2>11. Your Rights</h2>
        <div class="pv-text">
          <p>Under the GDPR, you have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Right of access</strong> (Art.&nbsp;15) — obtain confirmation and a copy of your data</li>
            <li><strong>Right to rectification</strong> (Art.&nbsp;16) — correct inaccurate data</li>
            <li><strong>Right to erasure</strong> (Art.&nbsp;17) — request deletion of your data</li>
            <li><strong>Right to restriction</strong> (Art.&nbsp;18) — limit how we process your data</li>
            <li><strong>Right to data portability</strong> (Art.&nbsp;20) — receive your data in a structured, machine-readable format</li>
            <li><strong>Right to object</strong> (Art.&nbsp;21) — object to processing based on legitimate interests</li>
            <li><strong>Right to withdraw consent</strong> (Art.&nbsp;7(3)) — where processing is based on consent, withdraw at any time without affecting prior lawfulness</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at
            <a href="mailto:office@tiptig.com">office@tiptig.com</a>.
            We will respond within one month of receiving your request.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Supervisory Authority -->
      <div class="pv-section reveal">
        <h2>12. Right to Lodge a Complaint</h2>
        <div class="pv-text">
          <p>
            If you believe that the processing of your personal data violates the GDPR,
            you have the right to lodge a complaint with the competent supervisory authority:
          </p>
          <div class="pv-contact-block">
            <p>
              <strong>Austrian Data Protection Authority</strong><br>
              (Österreichische Datenschutzbehörde)<br>
              Barichgasse 40–42<br>
              1030 Vienna, Austria
            </p>
            <p>
              Website: <a href="https://www.dsb.gv.at" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.dsb.gv.at</a><br>
              Email: <a href="mailto:dsb@dsb.gv.at">dsb@dsb.gv.at</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Changes -->
      <div class="pv-section pv-section-last reveal">
        <h2>13. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <div class="pv-text">
          <p>
            We reserve the right to update this privacy policy to reflect changes in our
            data processing practices or legal requirements. The current version is always
            available at this URL. We encourage you to review this page periodically.
          </p>
          <p class="pv-updated">Last updated: March 2026. The German-language version of this privacy policy shall prevail in case of discrepancies.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .pv-hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 160px 60px 80px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .pv-hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg) 0%, white 100%);
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .pv-hero .inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  .pv-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sapphire);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .pv-eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 24px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--sapphire);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--black);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .blue { color: var(--sapphire); }
  .pv-desc {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--gray-mid);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 600px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* Content */
  .pv-content {
    padding: 0 60px 96px;
  }
  .inner-pv {
    max-width: 860px;
  }

  .pv-section {
    padding: 40px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
  }
  .pv-section-last {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .pv-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--black);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  /* Text blocks */
  .pv-text p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--gray-mid);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .pv-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .pv-text p strong {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--black);
  }

  .pv-text ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
  }
  .pv-text ul li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--gray-mid);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-weight: 300;
    padding-left: 18px;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .pv-text ul li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 11px;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--sapphire);
    opacity: 0.4;
  }
  .pv-text ul li strong {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--black);
  }

  /* Contact block */
  .pv-contact-block {
    background: var(--bg);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin: 14px 0;
  }
  .pv-contact-block p {
    margin-bottom: 10px !important;
  }
  .pv-contact-block p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  }

  /* Links */
  .pv-text a,
  .pv-contact-block a {
    color: var(--sapphire);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .pv-text a:hover,
  .pv-contact-block a:hover {
    color: var(--sapphire-light);
  }

  .pv-updated {
    font-size: 0.85rem !important;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(107, 114, 128, 0.7) !important;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pv-hero { padding: 120px 24px 56px; }
    .pv-content { padding: 0 24px 72px; }
  }
</style>
